data.description: REMODELED 4-bed, 3.5-bath Liberty Hall Plantation home on large corner lot with double porches.  Brand new LVP flooring throughout!  Kitchen includes NEW quartz counters, roomy pantry, and separate dining area. The kitchen flows seamlessly into the great room with a chic bar-height counter. Downstairs, a spacious primary bedroom boasts an en-suite bath with a separate shower, tub, double sink vanity, and a walk-in closet. Upstairs, a versatile loft awaits, and bedrooms are thoughtfully separated. A third full bathroom and a convenient powder room complete the layout. Enjoy neighborhood amenities like a pool, playground, park, and sidewalks. Proximity to military bases, Boeing, Bosch, shopping, dining, and recreation adds convenience. All this and more. Schedule your private tour today
